o." Horm Metab Res 4 (1972):  64-8[3] DeFronzo RA, Cooke CR, Andres R, Faloona GR, Davis PJ "The effect of insulin on renal handling of sodium, potassium, calcium, and phosphate in man." J Clin Invest 55 (1975):  845-55', 1767365211);
