e inhibitors in depressed patients." Ther Drug Monit 23 (2001):  435-40[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[6] Pacher P, Kecskemeti V "Cardiovascular side effects of new antidepressants and antipsychotics: new drugs, old concerns?" Curr Pharm Des 10 (2004):  2463-75[7] Andrews C, Pinner G "Postural hypotension induced by paroxetine." BMJ 316 (1998):  595', 1767365211);
